room_title: Escape room "The Georgetown Morgue" by Seattle Escape Games in Seattle
room_description:
When you accepted the job as an assistant mortician of the Georgetown Morgue, you were excited! It doesn't take you long to figure out that something isn't quite right with your new boss. He is seriously giving you the creeps!
You build up the courage to leave, only to find yourself locked in the Morgue. The mortician has given subtle hints that when he returns in an hour, he may be expecting something from you, and it's not about work... Can you find your way out of the morgue and escape before time runs out, or will you be joining those who never leave?
